        <characteristic name="Succes" typeId="1ba0-f8a9-fa4d-9143">The targeted unit must make a leadership test. If failed it receives a Broken morale token and must move 2d6” away from the Psyker casting this power</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="Major Succes" typeId="dfc3-bf8a-d2f5-5a0d">You may target another unit with this power thats within 6” of the first target.</characteristic>
